===Noun===
'''[[功]][[夫]]'''
# time (to do something); synonym for [[工夫]]
# efforts (devoted to a task)
#: ''[[要]][[花]][[很]][[大]][[的]]'''功夫'''[[才]][[行]]''
#: ''it won't work unless one expends great effort''
# accomplishments
# skill; art (especially Chinese martial arts)
#: ''[[那]][[個]][[演員]][[念]][[台詞]][[的]]'''功夫'''[[不錯]]''
#: ''[[那]][[个]][[演员]][[念]][[台词]][[的]]'''功夫'''[[不错]]''
#: ''That actor's skill at reading his lines is not too [[shabby]]''
# [[kung fu]]
#: ''[[這]][[是]][[中國]][[少林]]'''功夫'''[[首次]][[在]][[雅典]][[登台]][[亮相]]''
#: ''[[这]][[是]][[中国]][[少林]]'''功夫'''[[首次]][[在]][[雅典]][[登台]][[亮相]]''[http://64.233.167.104/search?q=cache:p_HrL1PmCvIJ:www.ccdy.cn/pubnews/454017/20060714/496584.htm+%22%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%AB%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=29]
